	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil habeo nunc temporis, quod scribam; quę apud nos circumferebantur, iis diebus scripsi, et puto te meas recepisse a <placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Tigurino</placeName> quodam cive.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę in <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName> aguntur, poteris diligentissime perquirere a tabellario.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magedeburgum</placeName> gravissime obsidetur; sic ad me quidam scribit; literę datę sunt 29. maii: "Ante triduum vehementer conflixerunt; pugnę velitariae fere quotidie habentur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exercitus prope <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1750" cert="high">Luneburgum</placeName> iterum conspicitur; adversus quos, ignoratur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName> turbabitur gravissime hoc anno.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videntur multa prodigia; magnae sunt hominum desperationes, multi se suspendunt, confodiunt, suffocantur in aquis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Diaboli omnes in locis nostris grassantur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sodomus episcopus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1681" cert="high">Merseburgensis</placeName> in visitatione ecclesiarum concionaturus dysenteria ilice est correptus et gravissime decumbit."</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura percipies a tabellario, qui varia narraturus est de obsidione illa.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fortiter resistunt pii homines.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid agitur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21" cert="high">Badenę</placeName> in comitiis?</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Gumpenbergius</persName> nostros turbabit absque dubio, et bona ecclesiastica tandem, quod deus avertat, nobis magnum dabunt malum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cupio praeterea scire, an aliquid editurus sis hac aestate et quas nunc temporis cogitationes habeas, quas divulgare constituisti.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 20. iunii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodorum</persName> nomine meo salutabis, cui brevi scribam, quum literas ab <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> recepero, quas in omnia momenta expecto variis de rebus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l213">Hassia</placeName>, ne hoc praeteream, evangelii contio adhuc auditur clarissime, et vix 8 inveniuntur in tota illa regione, qui missentur.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Princeps adhuc durissima captivitate detinetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem ehrwurdigen herren m. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Heinrych Bullinger</persName>, lutpriester der kirchen zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>, mynem gunstigen herren, zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
